msgstr "Jo side is ynsteld om flaters oan te melden yn in mooglik iepenbier bestân"

#: wp-admin/includes/class-wp-site-health.php:1489
msgid "Debug mode is often enabled to gather more details about an error or site failure, but may contain sensitive information which should not be available on a publicly available website."
msgstr "Debug-modus is faak ynskeakele om mear details te sammeljen oer in flater of sitemislearring, mar kin gefoelige ynformaasje befetsje dy't net beskikber wêze moat op in publyklik beskikbere webside."

